a.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小黑冇白虎水馬火馬冇人權<br />\n天空隱形路行錯步屌撚曬鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機暴T技開左由廢寵變熱門 7日免費狂開新人拎機暴 \\<br />\n77金豬猜迷100答錯ON9死<br />\n2000青龍刷盜賊刷到想嘔<br />\n<br />\n後期都係係石像下 一堆人吹水多 隻GAME人緣最重要<br />\n未有騎証4大紅藍暴兩隻人一紅一藍 當年騎証一出直接問人拎就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾經既加加長老 不過都好後期 <br />\n<br />\n最想搵返既人係 笨叔叔,CWK 當年兩個好哥哥 <br />\n帶我福杓時代玩一齊拎紅暴好開心 有緣希望可以出黎再飲過茶<br />\n<br />\n重有7轉人(7仔) ,多口  都想搵下你地 有緣相認就出黎食下飯<br />\n<br />\n最FD既就係加加既 b仔 當年真係唔關我事 可惜我點講都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有其他人不能盡錄,技安,大哥,威敏兩公婆,223X,小DEE DEE,<br />\nFING頭小吉兩兄弟, 有限公司果堆人 阿清 其他已經唔記得名 <br />\n感謝你地令我有個開心既時段<br />\n<br />\n自爆下先 我係ming^^ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a2662b1b6e8886445808025ab5fc4ab26992f0","tid":2219672,"uid":111965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"220c1f7e5463ac0691d363af8f6ce7a8a84243c8","tid":2219672,"uid":362900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T00:09:41.000Z","msg":"記得去打80 象區, 要行去一邊, 之後用瞬間轉移跳過去 <br />\n<br />\n有無人有印象? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T00:16:15.000Z","msg":"牆角位起跳 低LV偷渡大法<br />\n入英雄島都係加人入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbe7e6fe93d90449028390188c900107b81837c","tid":2219672,"uid":111965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99e9e60a47ec56d32dcf00adf483f96842941e3e","tid":2219672,"uid":16937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"460ff286ce98745dea14cae43503aead32e3f86d","tid":2219672,"uid":7517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"幻界揮手區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T20:11:16.00